"title": "5549: speech, positive aspects of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5549: speech, positive aspects of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The way in which believers speak should reflect their calling as Christians. Christian speech should be sincere, godly and honouring to God.</p>\n<h2>The desire for godly speech</h2>\n<h3>In oneself</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:14\">PSA 19:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:3\">PSA 17:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:1\">PSA 39:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps141:3\">PSA 141:3</a></p>\n<h3>In others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:29-Eph4:31\">EPH 4:29–4:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:24\">PRO 4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:6\">ECC 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:4\">EPH 5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:8-Col3:10\">COL 3:8–3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:9-1Pet3:10\">1PE 3:9–3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:12-Ps34:13\">PSA 34:12–34:13</a></p>\n<h2>Characteristics of godly speech in relation to God</h2>\n<h3>It gives glory to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:15\">HEB 13:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:1\">PSA 34:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:28\">PSA 35:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:15\">PSA 51:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9\">1PE 2:9</a></p>\n<h3>It gives thanks and praise to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:17\">COL 3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:10\">DEU 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:4\">1CH 16:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:7-1Chr16:8\">1CH 16:7–16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:34-1Chr16:36\">1CH 16:34–16:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps100:4\">PSA 100:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:1\">PSA 118:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:19\">PSA 118:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:21\">PSA 118:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:28-Ps118:29\">PSA 118:28–118:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:26\">JOL 2:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:6-Mark8:7\">MRK 8:6–8:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:7\">COL 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:18\">1TH 5:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:9-Jas3:10\">JAS 3:9–3:10</a></p>\n<h3>It confesses Jesus Christ as Lord</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:9-Rom10:10\">ROM 10:9–10:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:32-Matt10:33\">MAT 10:32–10:33</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:8-Luke12:9\">LUK 12:8–12:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:16\">MAT 16:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:3\">1CO 12:3</a></p>\n<h2>Characteristics of godly speech in relation to others</h2>\n<h3>It is gentle, gracious and tactful</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:6\">COL 4:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:1-Judg8:3\">JDG 8:1–8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:32\">PRO 10:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:1\">PRO 15:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:24\">PRO 16:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:12\">ECC 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:14-Dan2:16\">DAN 2:14–2:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:15\">1PE 3:15</a></p>\n<h3>It is kind</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:25\">PRO 12:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:19-Gen50:21\">GEN 50:19–50:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:3-Job4:4\">JOB 4:3–4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:13\">1CO 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:24-2Tim2:25\">2TI 2:24–2:25</a></p>\n<h3>It is instructive and edifying</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:16\">COL 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:18\">PRO 12:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:2\">PRO 15:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:4\">PRO 15:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:7\">PRO 15:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:15\">PRO 20:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:11-Prov25:12\">PRO 25:11–25:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:26\">PRO 31:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:7\">MAL 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:15\">EPH 4:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:29\">EPH 4:29</a></p>\n<h3>It is prudent and restrained</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:27\">PRO 17:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:28\">PRO 15:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:13\">PRO 18:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:2\">ECC 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:17\">ECC 9:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:19\">JAS 1:19</a></p>\n<h3>It is honest and unadorned</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:37\">MAT 5:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps15:2-Ps15:3\">PSA 15:2–15:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps141:5\">PSA 141:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:26\">PRO 24:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:5-Prov27:6\">PRO 27:5–27:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:9\">PRO 27:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:23\">PRO 28:23</a></p>\n<h3>It is truthful and sincere</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:16\">ZEC 8:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:16\">EXO 20:16</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:20\">DEU 5:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:17\">PRO 12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:19\">PRO 12:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:22\">PRO 12:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:6\">MAL 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:17\">2CO 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:2\">2CO 4:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:7\">2CO 6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:25\">EPH 4:25</a></p>\n<h3>It is wise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:30\">PSA 37:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:13\">PRO 10:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:31\">PRO 10:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:14\">PRO 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:10\">ACT 6:10</a></p>\n<h3>It will speak of God and his works</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:6-Deut6:9\">DEU 6:6–6:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:9-Ps40:10\">PSA 40:9–40:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:7\">PSA 145:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:16\">MAL 3:16</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's speech was perfect and unique</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:46\">JHN 7:46</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:28-Matt7:29\">MAT 7:28–7:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:54\">MAT 13:54</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:2\">MRK 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:22\">LUK 4:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:22-1Pet2:23\">1PE 2:22–2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:9\">ISA 53:9</a></p>\n<h3>Speech as a means of blessing people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:22-Num6:27\">NUM 6:22–6:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:22\">GEN 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:28\">GEN 1:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:5\">DEU 21:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr23:13\">1CH 23:13</a></p>",
